quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  19,26,"Fakulee washrabee waqarree AAaynanfa-imma tarayinna mina albashari ahadan faqooleeinnee nathartu lirrahmani sawmanfalan okallima alyawma insiyya"
  19,27,"Faatat bihi qawmaha tahmiluhuqaloo ya maryamu laqad ji/ti shay-an fariyya"
  19,28,"Ya okhta haroona ma kanaabooki imraa saw-in wama kanat ommuki baghiyya"
  19,29,"Faasharat ilayhi qaloo kayfanukallimu man kana fee almahdi sabiyya"
  19,30,"Qala innee AAabdu Allahi ataniyaalkitaba wajaAAalanee nabiyya"
  19,31,"WajaAAalanee mubarakan aynamakuntu waawsanee bissalati wazzakatima dumtu hayya"
  19,32,"Wabarran biwalidatee walam yajAAalneejabbaran shaqiyya"
  19,33,"Wassalamu AAalayya yawmawulidtu wayawma amootu wayawma obAAathu hayya"
  19,34,"Thalika AAeesa ibnu maryamaqawla alhaqqi allathee feehi yamtaroon"
  19,35,"Ma kana lillahi anyattakhitha min waladin subhanahu itha qadaamran fa-innama yaqoolu lahu kun fayakoon"
  19,36,"Wa-inna Allaha rabbee warabbukum faAAbudoohuhatha siratun mustaqeem"
  19,37,"Fakhtalafa al-ahzabumin baynihim fawaylun lillatheena kafaroo min mashhadiyawmin AAatheem"
  19,38,"AsmiAA bihim waabsir yawma ya/toonanalakini aththalimoona alyawmafee dalalin mubeen"
